targets.formattedQuery: SELECT $timeSeries as t, count() FROM $table WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY t ORDER BY t
targets.query:
$columns(
    'PSR %sat %freq',
    avg(psr) psr)
FROM $table
WHERE
    sat = '$satgraph'
    AND freq IN ($freq)
targets.rawQuery:
SELECT t, groupArray((concat('PSR ', sat, ' ', freq), psr)) AS groupArr FROM ( SELECT (intDiv(time, (1)) * (1)) AS t, sat, freq, avg(psr) psr FROM rawdata.range
WHERE "d" >= toDate(1665925553) AND "d" <= toDate(1665925561) AND time >= toUInt64(1665925553 * 1000) AND time <= toUInt64(1665925561 * 1000) AND
    sat = 'GPS4'
    AND freq IN ('L1CA') GROUP BY t, sat, freq ORDER BY t, sat, freq) GROUP BY t ORDER BY t
